images.title: An a-maize-ing puzzle
images.caption: Corn maze in Saylorsburg, Pennsylvania
images.desc: All hail Mazezilla, a massive maze of corn found in the Poconos region of Pennsylvania. Spread over 11 acres, there is a different one to solve every year, making it a popular attraction each September and October for those who enjoy perplexing challenges on a giant scale.
